msg: A slightly modified patch from Patrick Antivackis "A way to generate no cache header for the views" (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-3091) - OFBIZ-3091

Patrick : The goal of this improvement is to allow at the view level, through setup in the controller.xml file, to generate no-cache http headers. Example is included for the showcart view of the ecommerce application.
JLR : I have commented out Patrick's example in controller and put a comment about its usage
